\m \bd ፵፱፡\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ወቦ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd እለ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ይቤሉ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ኅድጉ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ንርአይ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ለእመ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ይመጽእ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ኤልያስ\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ያድኅኖ።\bd*
